songs.title: Butterfly Effect (Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Murda on the beat so it's not nice
Yeah, yeah

[Verse 1]
Niggas be talkin' like bitches (damn)
Pillow talkin' mean you snitchin' (brr)
You better mind your business (business)
That's why you all in your feelings (huh, huh)
Yeah, I bought a coupe with no ceilings (huh)
I poured a four and I feel it (four)
I'm in the kitchen, it smell like Chitterlings (ugh)

[Chorus]
I'm takin' on a new path (huh)
Makin' them bricks take a bath
Lil bitty bitch, do the math (bitch)
Lil' nigga, who are you? (who you?)
Must be bulletproof (brrr)
This shit bigger than you (it big)
This shit bigger than you (yeah)
V.I.P. my squad (yeah), drop off all the gang (yeah)
V.I.P. the lane (skrrt), V.I.P. the chain (squad)
V.I.P. my squad (yeah), drop off all the gang (yeah)
V.I.P. the lane (skrrt), V.I.P. the chain

[Verse 2]
Uh, yeah, baller alert (brr)
Lil' bitty bitch, I don't call her alert (brr)
Uh, yeah, follow alert
Go get the fire when I'm callin' the Merc
Uh, yeah, profit come first
I whip the bank, the bank, it gon' vert (whip it)
Yeah, I bought a McLaren
I bought a McLaren, didn't wanna buy verts
Young nigga can't even afford you (ohh)
I get a PJ and board it (damn)
I'm goin' over the water (pew)
I collect watches like Hoarders (watches)
I really came out the soil (ballin')
I really came from the dirt (bottom)
Remember the gang come first (gang)
Birds sing like the Vert
